      <title>中东紧张局势升级，石油从抛售中恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势加剧，一艘船只在红海遭到袭击，并且有报道称以色列坦克已抵达拉法中心，油价从上周的抛售中反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 23:28:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
